{"tid":1142038,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法國東北部屢現反猶反移民塗鴉　市政府大樓遭殃","createTime":"2019-05-06T23:33:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-07T05:03:07.000Z","uid":141151,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0dfe6a6b722c1506945797661bda1e907b983e44","tid":1142038,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T23:33:48.000Z","msg":"東北部屢現反猶反移民塗鴉　市政府大樓遭殃<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190506/bkn-20190506090657762-0506_00912_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20190506%2Fbkn-20190506090657762-0506_00912_001.html&d=BbGirfR5U81eMP64OYU5HA2E5jpmEl9YQHmcT4noKO0%3D&h=0ead690b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190506/bkn-20190506090657762-0506_00912_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n法國東北部下萊茵省一市政府大樓和部分學校範圍，日前被發現塗上反猶和反移民塗鴉。當地警長和軍警較早時也遇到同樣騷擾，而且在該區不斷出現。 <br />\n<br />\n據報道，民眾上周五（3日）在埃伯斯明斯特鎮的市政府發現有關塗鴉，內容中除了反猶和反移民，也有極右成分。而在過去數月，下萊茵省和上萊茵省亦曾出現多次反猶和種族歧視塗鴉。 <br />\n<br />\n最近一次發生在4月中旬，迪耶方塔的市政府建築物被塗上這類塗鴉。數天後在希爾蒂盖姆市一名議員的獨立房屋，也被塗上納粹標誌和侮辱字句。"},{"pid":"eb696c1e99fa8ddbfb07e51756d3349086f6f7b0","tid":1142038,"uid":84926,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T00:25:49.000Z","msg":"物極必反<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81138b148f94af4b2181a96c7be7f3808455f35e","tid":1142038,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T02:50:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99eea3cd62b071130feaa71d997e68323e6e7123","tid":1142038,"uid":120064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T03:00:34.000Z","msg":"很猶，很不健康"},{"pid":"ff4bcdb784fc11c88dc378450dab3d973979779a","tid":1142038,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T05:03:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}